## Feature: Disable Hand Cursor on /resourcing

**Trigger:** Popup dropdown control  
**Scope:** /resourcing pages only (case-insensitive URL match)  
**Control:** Dropdown with "On/Off" options (default = On)  

**Behavior:**
- When enabled: Injects cursor-fix.css to force standard cursor
- When disabled: Removes cursor-fix.css
- Setting persisted via chrome.storage.sync

**CSS Implementation:**
```css
* {
    cursor: default !important;
}